.SS INFO
The \f[B]INFO\f[R] request returns global and connection statistics.
It has no extra parameters.
.PP
\f[B]INFO\f[R] reply will consist of a map with two keys,
\f[B]connection\f[R] and \f[B]global\f[R].
The values associated with those keys are themselves maps with,
respectively, connection and global stats.
